Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.32,0:01:55.17,SR Dialogue,Karen'sBro,0000,0000,0000,,Nee-chan, Nee-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.17,0:01:58.95,SR Dialogue,Karen'sBro,0000,0000,0000,,Today's the Dojibiron ofukai! You didn't forget, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.17,0:02:00.47,TL NOTES,Karen,0000,0000,0000,,Note: "Ofukai" is a term that is used when people who come to know each other through the Internet meet up in real life.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.95,0:02:00.47,SR Dialogue,Karen,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? Ofukai?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.83,0:02:02.60,SR Dialogue,Karen,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.60,0:02:06.50,SR Dialogue,Karen,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Onee-chan's worn out from her part-time job, so let me sleep today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.50,0:02:07.18,SR Dialogue,Bro,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.20,0:02:10.51,SR Dialogue,Bro,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.51,0:02:12.39,SR Dialogue,Bro,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be playing in the room. {TLC}{Cairan: i guess, he says ofutomo which means offline friend, i think; but even so the TL is correct}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.39,0:02:14.25,SR Dialogue,Karen,0000,0000,0000,,What? You're inviting him over?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.66,0:02:18.00,SR Dialogue,Bro,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, I'm the coordinator.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.00,0:02:21.45,SR Dialogue,Karen,0000,0000,0000,,Hm, the elementary schoolers these days are really something.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.97,0:02:26.23,SR Dialogue,Toy,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need it. I don't need it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.23,0:02:30.91,SR Dialogue,Karen,0000,0000,0000,,You meet lots of people you don't know on the Internet, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.91,0:02:32.98,SR Dialogue,Karen,0000,0000,0000,,What if someone weird comes?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.98,0:02:36.47,SR Dialogue,Bro,0000,0000,0000,,It's Dojibiron Blue, the one who's always writing to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.80,0:02:39.40,SR Dialogue,Karen,0000,0000,0000,,Hm... He's the guy that's pretty friendly with you, right, Kousuke?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.79,0:02:41.30,SR Dialogue,Karen,0000,0000,0000,,How old is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.30,0:02:44.31,SR Dialogue,Bro,0000,0000,0000,,He just uses hiragana, so he's probably younger than I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.81,0:02:47.17,SR Dialogue,Karen,0000,0000,0000,,Really? That's fine then.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.17,0:02:48.85,SR Dialogue,Karen,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you keep it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.85,0:02:50.31,SR Dialogue,Bro,0000,0000,0000,,I know, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.31,0:02:52.81,SR Dialogue,Karen,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, Onee-chan's going to sleep for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.81,0:02:53.78,SR Dialogue,Bro,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.21,0:03:06.79,SR Dialogue,Karen,0000,0000,0000,,Coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.44,0:03:10.27,SR Dialogue,Karen,0000,0000,0000,,Eh, I--Imadori-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.86,0:03:14.20,SR Dialogue,Imadori,0000,0000,0000,,Ichi-san, will you go out with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.20,0:03:19.24,SR Dialogue,Karen,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Uh... But um... Is it really alright that it's with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.45,0:03:23.37,SR Dialogue,Imadori,0000,0000,0000,,Ichi-san... No, Karen...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.12,0:03:26.50,SR Dialogue,Imadori,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like I've lost to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.10,0:03:32.01,SR Dialogue,Bro,0000,0000,0000,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.01,0:03:36.05,SR Dialogue,Imadori,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, so that's what you did... What should I...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.01,0:03:36.05,SR Dialogue,Karen,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\3c&H2F7EE0&}Owww... Huh? Huh? A d-dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.05,0:03:38.13,SR Dialogue,Bro,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Blue, you lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.07,0:03:39.19,SR Dialogue,Karen,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\3c&H2F7EE0&}Why did I have a dream like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.13,0:03:41.25,SR Dialogue,Imadori,0000,0000,0000,,Awww. Wait, wait. That last one didn't count.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.67,0:03:48.84,TL NOTES,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(84,0)}Note: Imadori mistakes "oujougiwa" (knowing to give up) with "ogyougi" (manners).
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.72,0:03:43.34,SR Dialogue,Karen,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\3c&H2F7EE0&}But it was a nice dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.25,0:03:42.95,SR Dialogue,Imadori,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, let's go for another round.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.95,0:03:44.67,SR Dialogue,Bro,0000,0000,0000,,You really don't know when to quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.67,0:03:46.74,SR Dialogue,Karen,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\3c&H2F7EE0&}They're really noisy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.74,0:03:47.49,SR Dialogue,Imadori,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Why? I have good manners.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.49,0:03:48.84,SR Dialogue,Bro,0000,0000,0000,,I said you don't know when to quit!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.49,0:03:51.21,SR Dialogue,Karen,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\3c&H2F7EE0&}Hey, Kousuke! Keep it down a bi--
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.84,0:03:51.71,SR Dialogue,Imadori,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, it's time for a comeback with Unprecedented mode.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.51,0:03:53.42,SR Dialogue,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,This!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.84,0:03:55.39,SR Dialogue,Bro,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Nee-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.39,0:03:56.75,SR Dialogue,Imadori,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Nee-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.48,0:04:01.11,SR Dialogue,Karen,0000,0000,0000,,W--W--W--W--Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.11,0:04:02.99,SR Dialogue,Karen,0000,0000,0000,,W--Why is I--Ima...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.99,0:04:04.38,SR Dialogue,Bro,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Nee-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.38,0:04:06.18,SR Dialogue,Bro,0000,0000,0000,,He's Dojibiron Blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.03,0:04:08.01,SR Dialogue,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.51,0:04:10.47,SR Dialogue,Karen,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Imadori-san is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.81,0:04:12.60,SR Dialogue,Karen,0000,0000,0000,,But you said he was younger than you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.60,0:04:15.45,SR Dialogue,Bro,0000,0000,0000,,Before that, why do you know his name?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.45,0:04:19.00,SR Dialogue,Karen,0000,0000,0000,,W-Why? Because he's a guy in my class!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.00,0:04:21.52,SR Dialogue,Bro,0000,0000,0000,,No way! This hilarious guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.52,0:04:23.60,SR Dialogue,Bro,0000,0000,0000,,Nee-chan's so lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.12,0:04:26.39,SR Dialogue,Karen,0000,0000,0000,,W--Wait, first...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.39,0:04:27.03,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.46,0:04:29.15,SR Dialogue,Karen,0000,0000,0000,,We have to do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.15,0:04:30.16,SR Dialogue,Bro,0000,0000,0000,,Do what?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.01,0:04:33.87,SR Dialogue,Karen,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know! Do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.56,0:04:35.54,SR Dialogue,Green,0000,0000,0000,,There, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.54,0:04:39.02,SR Dialogue,Karen,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh! The dirty clothes are everywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.02,0:04:41.44,SR Dialogue,Bro,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares? It's just dirty clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.44,0:04:43.01,SR Dialogue,Karen,0000,0000,0000,,Just come help me already!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.31,0:04:45.01,SR Dialogue,Karen,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and fold them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.47,0:04:47.01,SR Dialogue,Karen,0000,0000,0000,,Put them away! Put them away!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.01,0:04:48.93,SR Dialogue,Imadori,0000,0000,0000,,Ichi-san, what about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.93,0:04:51.39,SR Dialogue,Karen,0000,0000,0000,,Um, that goes in the bottom-most drawer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.10,0:04:54.15,SR Dialogue,Karen,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, Imadori-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.15,0:04:57.16,SR Dialogue,Imadori,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I thought I should help out, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.16,0:05:00.59,SR Dialogue,Imadori,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, why do you have such a big one?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.59,0:05:02.29,SR Dialogue,Karen,0000,0000,0000,,That belongs to my mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.29,0:05:04.86,SR Dialogue,Imadori,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, Ichi-san's mom has a nice body?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.56,0:05:07.78,SR Dialogue,Imadori,0000,0000,0000,,I found Ichi-san's pajamas.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.11,0:05:10.25,SR Dialogue,Karen,0000,0000,0000,,G--Give those back, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.25,0:05:14.20,SR Dialogue,Imadori,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Ichi-san, aren't these dumbbells a bit too heavy? I can't lift them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.20,0:05:16.79,SR Dialogue,Karen,0000,0000,0000,,You're lying! You're lying! They're only five kilos!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.79,0:05:21.75,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\be1\fs26\frz32\bord0\shad0\c&H1C545D&\fnArial Narrow\pos(242,40)}Target
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.29,0:05:19.55,SR Dialogue,Imadori,0000,0000,0000,,Hm, your target is the first half of the forties?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.55,0:05:21.32,SR Dialogue,Imadori,0000,0000,0000,,A bit more and your diet will be a success.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.32,0:05:21.75,SR Dialogue,Imadori,0000,0000,0000,,Keep it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.75,0:05:21.80,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\be1\fs24\frz32\bord0\shad0\c&H1C545D&\fnArial Narrow\pos(281,36)}Target
