Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.84,0:05:21.88,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\be1\fs20\frz32\bord0\shad0\c&H1C545D&\fnArial Narrow\pos(356,29)}Target
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.88,0:05:21.92,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\be1\fs18\frz32\bord0\shad0\c&H1C545D&\fnArial Narrow\pos(382,26)}Target
