Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.76,0:05:24.51,SR Dialogue,Karen,0000,0000,0000,,Stop looking!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.51,0:05:26.38,SR Dialogue,Karen,0000,0000,0000,,You're the worst, Imadori-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.38,0:05:29.46,SR Dialogue,Imadori,0000,0000,0000,,Hehe, I got called "the worst" by Ichi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.46,0:05:31.44,SR Dialogue,Karen,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it already!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.44,0:05:34.70,SR Dialogue,Bro,0000,0000,0000,,Nee-chan, forget about that and let's play pretend Dojibiron.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.70,0:05:37.28,SR Dialogue,Bro,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be Pink, like you always are.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.28,0:05:40.11,SR Dialogue,Imadori,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Ichi-san's Pink sounds pretty strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.82,0:05:43.73,SR Dialogue,Imadori,0000,0000,0000,,Ichi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.57,0:05:47.28,SR Dialogue,Imadori,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. Just do it like you always do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.98,0:05:50.28,SR Dialogue,Imadori,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to see that Ichi-san as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.26,0:05:52.47,SR Dialogue,Karen,0000,0000,0000,,Imadori-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.33,0:05:55.69,SR Dialogue,Karen,0000,0000,0000,,Then... Then just for a bit... {Cairan: the mark on Karen's head means 'hot spring'"}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.69,0:05:56.71,SR Dialogue,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.46,0:05:59.58,SR Dialogue,Karen,0000,0000,0000,,Collision!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.04,0:06:01.62,SR Dialogue,Karen,0000,0000,0000,,Combination!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.33,0:06:08.09,SR Dialogue,Karen,0000,0000,0000,,Dojibiron!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.44,0:06:12.81,SR Dialogue,Karen,0000,0000,0000,,Episode Thirty-four:
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.81,0:06:17.72,SR Dialogue,Karen,0000,0000,0000,,The Massage Monster Ryuusan and the Hidden Trap in a Three-Night, Four-Day Field Trip - Second Half.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.72,0:06:18.79,SR Dialogue,Bro,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.79,0:06:21.90,SR Dialogue,Imadori,0000,0000,0000,,Choosing the phantom in the thirty-fourth episode... You know your stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.48,0:06:26.62,SR Dialogue,Bro,0000,0000,0000,,Ahhh, a massage after a bath is the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.12,0:06:27.86,SR Dialogue,Bro,0000,0000,0000,,My body...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.34,0:06:29.86,SR Dialogue,Karen,0000,0000,0000,,Keep it together, Squad Member Kousuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.55,0:06:33.99,SR Dialogue,Bro,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it, I'm mutilated after the massage...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.26,0:06:38.71,SR Dialogue,Imadori,0000,0000,0000,,Muahahahaha, you're next.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.71,0:06:41.30,SR Dialogue,Bro,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this is where Ryuusan jumps in!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.30,0:06:43.68,SR Dialogue,Imadori,0000,0000,0000,,I'll suck your fighting spirit out, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.12,0:06:47.42,SR Dialogue,Imadori,0000,0000,0000,,Momi, momi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.12,0:06:47.42,TL NOTES,Imadori,0000,0000,0000,,Note: "Momi, momi!" is "Massage, massage!"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.42,0:06:49.13,SR Dialogue,Bro,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do, Squad Member Karen?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.13,0:06:49.84,SR Dialogue,Karen,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.32,0:06:52.85,SR Dialogue,Karen,0000,0000,0000,,Take this! Unprecedented Hammer! {Cairan: hatenkou is again "unprecedented", but we may leave it as it is}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.52,0:06:57.60,SR Dialogue,Imadori,0000,0000,0000,,Ohhh, you have some skill, Dojibiron.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.60,0:06:59.87,SR Dialogue,Karen,0000,0000,0000,,As expected of Ryuusan. He's tough!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.72,0:07:04.98,SR Dialogue,All,0000,0000,0000,,One plus one is two.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.73,0:07:08.42,SR Dialogue,All,0000,0000,0000,,Two plus two is four.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.76,0:07:11.75,SR Dialogue,All,0000,0000,0000,,If one more were to come out,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.75,0:07:13.88,SR Dialogue,All,0000,0000,0000,,Five! Five, five, five!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.88,0:07:15.43,SR Dialogue,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Doryaa!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.43,0:07:16.78,SR Dialogue,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Soyaa!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.34,0:07:20.66,SR Dialogue,Karen,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry about the ruckus today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.86,0:07:27.00,SR Dialogue,Karen,0000,0000,0000,,However, if you told me beforehand that you were coming, I would have been better prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.35,0:07:29.09,SR Dialogue,Bro,0000,0000,0000,,Come by again, Blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.09,0:07:31.42,SR Dialogue,Imadori,0000,0000,0000,,Sure. I'll be back, Kousuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.42,0:07:33.42,SR Dialogue,Imadori,0000,0000,0000,,Don't cause trouble for your sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.42,0:07:34.51,SR Dialogue,Bro,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.62,0:07:46.73,SR Dialogue,Bro,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Nee-chan, why don't you go out with Blue?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.73,0:07:47.93,SR Dialogue,Bro,0000,0000,0000,,Just kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.72,0:07:49.19,SR Dialogue,Bro,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.20,0:07:53.16,SR Dialogue,Bro,0000,0000,0000,,Hm...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.30,0:07:58.49,SR Dialogue,Bro,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Nee-chan, isn't this mask the one that Blue brought over?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.88,0:08:02.40,SR Dialogue,Karen,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? But I thought I just saw Imadori-san put that in his pocket...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.30,0:08:17.43,SR Dialogue,Fuyuki,0000,0000,0000,,The sound recording and angle are both set.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.43,0:08:19.56,SR Dialogue,Fuyuki,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, we're good to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.56,0:08:21.68,SR Dialogue,Fuyuki,0000,0000,0000,,All that's left is to turn the camera around.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.28,0:08:26.00,SR Dialogue,Yuuki,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you. You came to help even though it's winter break.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.00,0:08:29.15,SR Dialogue,Fuyuki,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it. It's just some good will from a fellow band member.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.78,0:08:32.86,SR Dialogue,Fuyuki,0000,0000,0000,,It's cold out here. You can go back to the clubroom if you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.26,0:08:37.32,SR Dialogue,Yuuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine. This is the only time I'll have to look at the stars anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.73,0:08:46.71,SR Dialogue,Fuyuki,0000,0000,0000,,Next year will be our third. Are you planning to go down the astronomy path, Yuuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.71,0:08:47.17,SR Dialogue,Yuuki,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.34,0:08:51.01,TL NOTES,Fuyuki,0000,0000,0000,,Note: High school in Japan is split into Social sciences and Natural sciences. She says she can't take the astronomy path because she is part of the social sciences group.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.34,0:08:51.01,SR Dialogue,Yuuki,0000,0000,0000,,I like the stars, but I'm a social science student.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.20,0:08:54.09,SR Dialogue,Fuyuki,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.56,0:08:57.68,SR Dialogue,Sagano,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, it's freezing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.20,0:08:59.87,SR Dialogue,Sagano,0000,0000,0000,,It has really gotten cold today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.17,0:09:01.72,SR Dialogue,Sagano,0000,0000,0000,,I brought some snacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.56,0:09:05.44,SR Dialogue,Sagano,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? Did I tell you about today's meeting?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.05,0:09:09.33,SR Dialogue,Yuuki,0000,0000,0000,,I asked him to come lend a hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.00,0:09:10.81,SR Dialogue,Sagano,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.56,0:09:13.57,SR Dialogue,Sagano,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever. Let's eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.57,0:09:15.66,SR Dialogue,Fuyuki,0000,0000,0000,,As expected of Sagano. You're quite the thoughtful one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.03,0:09:18.41,SR Dialogue,Sagano,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I am the daughter of a Japanese cuisine restaurant owner.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.84,0:09:20.12,SR Dialogue,Sagano,0000,0000,0000,,Voila!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.06,0:09:30.34,SR Dialogue,Sagano,0000,0000,0000,,Well, now that we're all warmed up,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.34,0:09:32.61,SR Dialogue,Sagano,0000,0000,0000,,let's begin this year's telling of love stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.61,0:09:36.15,SR Dialogue,Karen,0000,0000,0000,,Eeh? Since when did that become a tradition?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.15,0:09:39.77,SR Dialogue,Sagano,0000,0000,0000,,Think about it. If three girls are gathered in a place like this at the end of a year,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.77,0:09:41.53,SR Dialogue,Sagano,0000,0000,0000,,what else is there to talk about?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.53,0:09:43.72,SR Dialogue,Fuyuki,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I'm here too, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.72,0:09:45.38,SR Dialogue,Fuyuki,0000,0000,0000,,They didn't hear me at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.38,0:09:47.57,SR Dialogue,Karen,0000,0000,0000,,Then what about you, Sagano?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.57,0:09:50.41,SR Dialogue,Sagano,0000,0000,0000,,Hehe, it's about time you asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.41,0:09:53.48,SR Dialogue,Sagano,0000,0000,0000,,I've matched up a total of ten couples this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.48,0:09:55.23,SR Dialogue,Sagano,0000,0000,0000,,It's a new record.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.23,0:09:57.15,SR Dialogue,Karen,0000,0000,0000,,You're so sly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.15,0:10:00.55,SR Dialogue,Karen,0000,0000,0000,,That's one part of you that has never changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.55,0:10:02.87,SR Dialogue,Sagano,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you haven't changed much either, Ichijou.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.51,0:10:06.14,SR Dialogue,Karen,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think so too? Somehow...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.14,0:10:09.38,SR Dialogue,Karen,0000,0000,0000,,While I was sitting around doing nothing, the whole year passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.71,0:10:13.33,SR Dialogue,Sagano,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true. Lots of things must have happened to you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.33,0:10:17.51,SR Dialogue,Sagano,0000,0000,0000,,Like when you sang in front of Imadori-kun, and when you called Imadori-kun to your house.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.51,0:10:20.36,SR Dialogue,Karen,0000,0000,0000,,N-No! That was Kousuke's doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.36,0:10:23.31,SR Dialogue,Yuuki,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. The fact is that Ichijou tried her best.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.31,0:10:25.76,SR Dialogue,Sagano,0000,0000,0000,,What about you, Yuuki? How was your year?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.76,0:10:26.47,SR Dialogue,Yuuki,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.83,0:10:32.02,SR Dialogue,Yuuki,0000,0000,0000,,I... didn't really do anything in particular.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.43,0:10:41.74,SR Dialogue,Yuuki,0000,0000,0000,,Watching you people shine brightly along with the stars... I guess that's all I can manage for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.08,0:10:46.77,SR Dialogue,Fuyuki,0000,0000,0000,,But man, it really has gotten cold. I'll go buy some coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.77,0:10:47.06,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.06,0:10:47.66,SR Dialogue,Fuyuki,0000,0000,0000,,You all want some?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.14,0:10:48.93,SR Dialogue,Sagano,0000,0000,0000,,Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.93,0:10:49.58,SR Dialogue,Fuyuki,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.58,0:10:51.82,SR Dialogue,Sagano,0000,0000,0000,,Leave that to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.21,0:10:53.68,SR Dialogue,Sagano,0000,0000,0000,,You two should just wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.68,0:10:54.63,SR Dialogue,Sagano,0000,0000,0000,,These chances don't come often.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.40,0:10:57.60,SR Dialogue,Sagano,0000,0000,0000,,This might be my eleventh.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.60,0:10:58.09,SR Dialogue,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.54,0:11:03.74,SR Dialogue,Yuuki,0000,0000,0000,,That was sort of a weird misunderstanding on Sagano's part.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.15,0:11:07.61,SR Dialogue,Fuyuki,0000,0000,0000,,Really? I'm quite fine with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.26,0:11:10.42,SR Dialogue,Yuuki,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. I'll pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.96,0:11:11.93,SR Dialogue,Fuyuki,0000,0000,0000,,I guess that didn't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.54,0:11:15.34,SR Dialogue,Yuuki,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like that air of confidence around you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.68,0:11:19.23,SR Dialogue,Fuyuki,0000,0000,0000,,No, no. Despite what you may think, I'm actually quite the naive guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.55,0:11:23.70,SR Dialogue,Yuuki,0000,0000,0000,,I know what you're like. You're very conscious of the public eye, and you desperately try to conduct yourself properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.70,0:11:25.90,SR Dialogue,Yuuki,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, you're still dishonest and insincere on the inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.46,0:11:28.85,SR Dialogue,Fuyuki,0000,0000,0000,,Hahahaha, that's harsh.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.85,0:11:30.86,SR Dialogue,Fuyuki,0000,0000,0000,,So that's what I look like to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.51,0:11:34.79,SR Dialogue,Yuuki,0000,0000,0000,,Just because I'm a plain social science girl doesn't mean I want to be looked down upon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.62,0:11:39.90,SR Dialogue,Fuyuki,0000,0000,0000,,Did... something happen today?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.90,0:11:40.92,SR Dialogue,Yuuki,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.92,0:11:42.21,SR Dialogue,Yuuki,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand you at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.46,0:11:46.26,SR Dialogue,Fuyuki,0000,0000,0000,,That part of you is really cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.17,0:11:50.76,SR Dialogue,Yuuki,0000,0000,0000,,Those words... You've said them to Sawachika-san as well, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.76,0:11:53.05,SR Dialogue,Fuyuki,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it wasn't only to Sawachika.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.45,0:11:55.77,SR Dialogue,Fuyuki,0000,0000,0000,,Every girl in love is beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.46,0:11:58.16,SR Dialogue,Fuyuki,0000,0000,0000,,I can see that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.68,0:12:00.74,SR Dialogue,Yuuki,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you're taking those pictures, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.74,0:12:01.93,SR Dialogue,Fuyuki,0000,0000,0000,,Nope. It's the opposite.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.93,0:12:04.62,SR Dialogue,Fuyuki,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to capture that beauty in my pictures.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.62,0:12:05.95,SR Dialogue,Fuyuki,0000,0000,0000,,But they never come out properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.29,0:12:08.61,SR Dialogue,Fuyuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a lucky guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.22,0:12:12.97,SR Dialogue,Fuyuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'll live on knowing that no one but I can see that beauty and I'll always have it all to myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.78,0:12:17.05,SR Dialogue,Fuyuki,0000,0000,0000,,You seem to be trapped in a spiral today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.67,0:12:19.34,SR Dialogue,Fuyuki,0000,0000,0000,,A spiral of sound and light.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.34,0:12:21.85,SR Dialogue,Yuuki,0000,0000,0000,,Stop that dubious fortune telling.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.04,0:12:32.64,SR Dialogue,Hanai,0000,0000,0000,,H--Hey, Suou!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.44,0:12:36.62,SR Dialogue,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, let's go over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.62,0:12:37.20,SR Dialogue,Hanai,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.25,0:12:47.79,SR Dialogue,Fuyuki,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I found a star.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.40,0:12:51.07,SR Dialogue,Yuuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. It's so far...
