Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.22,0:13:01.36,SR Dialogue,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what do you think of the new chief?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.36,0:13:03.98,SR Dialogue,Yakumo,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.98,0:13:06.39,SR Dialogue,Eri,0000,0000,0000,,I think he's fine. He's pretty handsome, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.39,0:13:09.52,SR Dialogue,Eri,0000,0000,0000,,It's a huge step up from the perverted old geezer we had.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.52,0:13:11.79,SR Dialogue,Eri,0000,0000,0000,,Although his taste in clothing is debatable...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.79,0:13:12.91,SR Dialogue,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's black.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.91,0:13:16.37,SR Dialogue,Eri,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe the black is part of some cultural dress?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.94,0:13:18.78,SR Dialogue,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't black fine?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.38,0:13:21.22,SR Dialogue,All,0000,0000,0000,,Heh heh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.22,0:13:22.36,SR Dialogue,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.36,0:13:23.60,SR Dialogue,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.60,0:13:24.77,SR Dialogue,Eri,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.77,0:13:27.30,SR Dialogue,Yakumo,0000,0000,0000,,Tenma, don't tell me it's love at first sight?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.30,0:13:28.37,SR Dialogue,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,W--W--What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.05,0:13:30.83,SR Dialogue,Karasuma,0000,0000,0000,,I'm thirsty.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.82,0:13:34.08,SR Dialogue,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I'll go make some tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.08,0:13:35.04,SR Dialogue,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, just a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.92,0:13:37.25,SR Dialogue,Eri,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.33,0:13:40.26,SR Dialogue,Eri,0000,0000,0000,,She's quite cheeky for a newcomer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.26,0:13:42.09,SR Dialogue,Eri,0000,0000,0000,,How can she seduce her superior?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.21,0:13:46.05,TL NOTES,Eri,0000,0000,0000,,Text: Saboka
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.66,0:13:45.40,SR Dialogue,Eri,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's time for the customary welcoming for new members of the Cyborg Department.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.35,0:13:51.56,SR Dialogue,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Tsukamoto Tenma, a newcomer at the cyborg department, commonly known as Saboka.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.51,0:13:52.14,TL NOTES,,0000,0000,0000,,Sign: Currently Boiling
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.56,0:13:54.50,SR Dialogue,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,I've only been allowed to prepare tea so far, but
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.50,0:13:56.71,SR Dialogue,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,with this 10,000 yen per 100 grams of tea,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.50,0:13:56.71,TL NOTES,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,Note: 10,000 Yen is about $100 USD.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.71,0:13:59.06,SR Dialogue,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,I'll win over Chief Karasuma's heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.67,0:14:01.07,SR Dialogue,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,Get out of the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.82,0:14:05.26,SR Dialogue,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is that I don't have any memories from over half a year ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.26,0:14:07.11,SR Dialogue,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, I have amnesia.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.49,0:14:10.62,SR Dialogue,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,Without a single relative, I drowned in loneliness.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.62,0:14:13.41,SR Dialogue,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,That was when Yakumo-oneechan held out her hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.41,0:14:18.55,SR Dialogue,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,Yakumo-oneechan is probably the oldest,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.55,0:14:20.92,SR Dialogue,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,so I affectionately call her Onee-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.34,0:14:24.67,SR Dialogue,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,This is the super ojou-sama-like Eri-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.01,0:14:28.87,SR Dialogue,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,This is the extremely large-breasted Mikoto-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.53,0:14:33.47,SR Dialogue,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,This is the cool, tomboy-looking Akira-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.75,0:14:38.04,SR Dialogue,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,It feels great to be surrounded by these people. I'm trying my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.12,0:14:40.81,SR Dialogue,Karasuma,0000,0000,0000,,This girl is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.81,0:14:42.77,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\shad0\c&H4F4F4F&\frz318.675\frx42\fry10\pos(494,105)}Tea Serving Chart
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.81,0:14:42.77,TL NOTES,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\bord0\shad0\c&H4F4F4F&}Names from left to right:\NSawachika Eri, Suou Mikoto, Tsukamoto Yakumo, Tsukamoto Tenma
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.39,0:14:48.28,SR Dialogue,Eri,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Chief, let's have dinner at the hotel tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.64,0:14:53.45,SR Dialogue,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,I spilled it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.29,0:15:00.00,SR Dialogue,Eri,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph, go remake it. While you're at it, make one for me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.64,0:15:02.42,SR Dialogue,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,Eri-senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.77,0:15:08.88,SR Dialogue,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,Pushing people around just because you have some extra cash...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.88,0:15:10.19,SR Dialogue,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,Take this! And this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.19,0:15:12.97,SR Dialogue,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world was I doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.45,0:15:16.59,SR Dialogue,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,Well, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.59,0:15:20.01,SR Dialogue,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,This time, I'll make Chief Karasuma drink my tea of love.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.01,0:15:23.11,SR Dialogue,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,Chief! Eri-senpai! The tea's ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.57,0:15:28.24,SR Dialogue,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,Chief, how do I write these documents?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.25,0:15:42.70,SR Dialogue,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,Getting all cocky just because your breasts are a bit bigger...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.70,0:15:44.13,SR Dialogue,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,Take this, and this, and this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.56,0:15:49.17,SR Dialogue,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,Again?! What was I doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.14,0:15:52.68,SR Dialogue,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be because of something in the past that I don't remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.22,0:15:57.45,SR Dialogue,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.45,0:15:59.93,SR Dialogue,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,Hehe. This time, I'll make sure you drink it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.27,0:16:05.18,SR Dialogue,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,The tea's ready, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.18,0:16:06.57,SR Dialogue,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,G-Gyooo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.00,0:16:09.37,SR Dialogue,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,Even Y-Yakumo-oneechan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.37,0:16:11.41,SR Dialogue,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,I--I believed in you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.41,0:16:14.78,SR Dialogue,Yakumo,0000,0000,0000,,N--No, this is... I had no choice...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.78,0:16:16.98,SR Dialogue,Yakumo,0000,0000,0000,,It's the customary welcoming party for newcomers.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.98,0:16:19.59,SR Dialogue,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,W--What part of that is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.06,0:16:22.42,SR Dialogue,Yakumo,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Tenma!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.98,0:16:27.92,SR Dialogue,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,So this is the rumored bullying of newcomers at Saboka!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.92,0:16:29.51,TL NOTES,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}Left: Cyborg Department\NRight: Cyberterrorism Department
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.55,0:16:33.88,SR Dialogue,Harima,0000,0000,0000,,Hot...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.88,0:16:35.33,SR Dialogue,Harima,0000,0000,0000,,Tenma-chan's tea...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.92,0:16:36.87,SR Dialogue,Lala,0000,0000,0000,,Should we do it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.87,0:16:37.14,SR Dialogue,Harima,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.78,0:16:39.60,SR Dialogue,Lala,0000,0000,0000,,Should Sabaka have a welcoming party too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.78,0:16:39.60,TL NOTES,Lala,0000,0000,0000,,Note: "Sabaka" is the name for the "Cyberterrorism Department."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.19,0:16:45.63,SR Dialogue,Harima,0000,0000,0000,,Why the hell did I end up as your superior?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.63,0:16:48.72,SR Dialogue,Harima,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how you look at it, you two should obviously be in the cyborg department!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.72,0:16:50.59,SR Dialogue,Karen,0000,0000,0000,,That's... so mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.16,0:16:53.86,SR Dialogue,Lala,0000,0000,0000,,You... made Ichijou cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.71,0:16:59.98,SR Dialogue,Harima,0000,0000,0000,,That bastard, bullying around my dear Tenma-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.98,0:17:01.60,SR Dialogue,Harima,0000,0000,0000,,Unforgivable!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.98,0:17:02.41,SR Dialogue,Eri,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.82,0:17:03.41,SR Dialogue,Harima,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.84,0:17:05.04,SR Dialogue,Eri,0000,0000,0000,,*Sweat* *Sweat*
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.96,0:17:08.09,SR Dialogue,Harima,0000,0000,0000,,Not you, you dumbass!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.63,0:17:14.01,SR Dialogue,Karen,0000,0000,0000,,W--Wait, Lala-san, he's choking!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.62,0:17:16.47,SR Dialogue,Akira,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.76,0:17:18.83,SR Dialogue,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,Akira-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.83,0:17:19.43,SR Dialogue,Akira,0000,0000,0000,,Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.66,0:17:22.63,SR Dialogue,Akira,0000,0000,0000,,I see... So that's what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.51,0:17:26.29,SR Dialogue,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a clumsy, stupid turtle.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.13,0:17:30.10,SR Dialogue,Akira,0000,0000,0000,,Heh, that's not like you at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.10,0:17:30.86,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.86,0:17:33.71,SR Dialogue,Akira,0000,0000,0000,,The girl I know as Tsukamoto Tenma is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.06,0:17:36.69,SR Dialogue,Akira,0000,0000,0000,,...a good girl who's always cheerful, overly energetic,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.69,0:17:39.70,SR Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and has enough overflowing vitality to share with other people.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.48,0:17:43.38,SR Dialogue,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,No way... That's just a show.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.38,0:17:48.29,SR Dialogue,Akira,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever it is, you cannot deny the fact that everyone is motivated by that vitality.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.05,0:17:49.58,SR Dialogue,Akira,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.77,0:17:53.72,SR Dialogue,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Yakumo-oneechan. Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.02,0:17:56.39,SR Dialogue,Yakumo,0000,0000,0000,,Tenma, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.39,0:17:59.82,SR Dialogue,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,We meant it as a joke. My bad, my bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.82,0:18:01.42,SR Dialogue,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.42,0:18:04.68,SR Dialogue,Eri,0000,0000,0000,,Um, ahem... I-It was our fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.12,0:18:11.07,SR Dialogue,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,H--Huh? What's going on? My eyes are watering for some reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.37,0:18:19.82,SR Dialogue,Karasuma,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. It was peaceful up until this point.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.73,0:18:24.22,SR Dialogue,Karasuma,0000,0000,0000,,However, there is something I must tell her,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.65,0:18:28.58,SR Dialogue,Karasuma,0000,0000,0000,,even if it means ripping apart that moment of happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.77,0:18:30.82,SR Dialogue,Karasuma,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukamoto-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.89,0:18:34.01,SR Dialogue,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,Chief K-Karasuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.88,0:18:41.14,SR Dialogue,Karasuma,0000,0000,0000,,There is something I must tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.33,0:18:47.56,SR Dialogue,Harima,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never forgive you, Karasuma. What the hell are you trying to...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.56,0:18:50.45,SR Dialogue,Lala,0000,0000,0000,,Chief Harima! Hurry up and finish your work!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.45,0:18:52.27,SR Dialogue,Harima,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! I'm doing something important her--
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.71,0:18:59.07,SR Dialogue,Eri,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.38,0:19:03.85,SR Dialogue,Yuuki,0000,0000,0000,,Something has infiltrated the network! It's trying to destroy the network!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.85,0:19:05.08,SR Dialogue,Karasuma,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, move out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.53,0:19:06.66,SR Dialogue,All,0000,0000,0000,,Understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.66,0:19:08.71,SR Dialogue,Harima,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it, that's my department, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.24,0:19:17.11,SR Dialogue,Karasuma,0000,0000,0000,,Roll call.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.11,0:19:17.52,SR Dialogue,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,One.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.52,0:19:17.85,SR Dialogue,Eri,0000,0000,0000,,Two.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.85,0:19:18.17,SR Dialogue,Akira,0000,0000,0000,,Three.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.17,0:19:18.54,SR Dialogue,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,Four.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.54,0:19:18.84,SR Dialogue,Yakumo,0000,0000,0000,,Five.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.84,0:19:19.26,SR Dialogue,Lala,0000,0000,0000,,Six!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.26,0:19:19.96,SR Dialogue,Karen,0000,0000,0000,,Seven.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.96,0:19:20.77,SR Dialogue,Karasuma,0000,0000,0000,,Again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.77,0:19:21.17,SR Dialogue,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,One.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.17,0:19:21.49,SR Dialogue,Eri,0000,0000,0000,,Two.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.49,0:19:21.79,SR Dialogue,Akira,0000,0000,0000,,Three.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.79,0:19:22.17,SR Dialogue,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,Four.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.17,0:19:22.47,SR Dialogue,Yakumo,0000,0000,0000,,Five.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.47,0:19:22.88,SR Dialogue,Lala,0000,0000,0000,,Six!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.88,0:19:23.10,SR Dialogue,Karen,0000,0000,0000,,Seven.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.81,0:19:25.97,SR Dialogue,Karasuma,0000,0000,0000,,An unprecendented crisis presses upon us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.44,0:19:28.60,SR Dialogue,Karasuma,0000,0000,0000,,You are the only ones who can remedy the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.60,0:19:29.35,SR Dialogue,Karasuma,0000,0000,0000,,Let's move.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.35,0:19:30.51,SR Dialogue,All,0000,0000,0000,,Understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.28,0:19:33.06,SR Dialogue,Harima,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, damn it! I said that's my job!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.40,0:19:35.94,SR Dialogue,Hanai,0000,0000,0000,,Ha ha ha ha ha ha ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.94,0:19:37.86,SR Dialogue,Hanai,0000,0000,0000,,I've been waiting for you, my dear cyborg girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.86,0:19:39.26,SR Dialogue,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,Professor Hanai!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.26,0:19:42.02,SR Dialogue,Hanai,0000,0000,0000,,Today will be the day I delete you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.02,0:19:43.99,SR Dialogue,Hanai,0000,0000,0000,,Go, my minions!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.89,0:19:47.20,SR Dialogue,Eri,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.55,0:19:49.96,SR Dialogue,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't sting me there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.40,0:19:52.67,SR Dialogue,Yakumo,0000,0000,0000,,Um... This is quite troubling...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.03,0:19:55.38,SR Dialogue,Karen,0000,0000,0000,,No! Please, stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.99,0:20:00.76,SR Dialogue,Lala,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.20,0:20:05.26,SR Dialogue,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,E--Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.73,0:20:07.00,SR Dialogue,Karen,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukamoto-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.30,0:20:08.56,SR Dialogue,Mikoto,0000,0000,0000,,Surmount our...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.56,0:20:10.17,SR Dialogue,Eri,0000,0000,0000,,Deaths and...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.53,0:20:11.56,SR Dialogue,Akira,0000,0000,0000,,Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.92,0:20:15.27,SR Dialogue,Yakumo,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone... really liked you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.77,0:20:17.74,SR Dialogue,Lala,0000,0000,0000,,TENMA!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.44,0:20:20.95,SR Dialogue,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,I'll carry on the spirit of your lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.52,0:20:23.49,SR Dialogue,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,Now I can fight with determination.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.87,0:20:25.45,SR Dialogue,Karasuma,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on, Tsukamoto-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.01,0:20:28.83,SR Dialogue,Karasuma,0000,0000,0000,,There is something I must tell you before the final battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.58,0:20:32.37,SR Dialogue,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be... about my forgotten past?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.25,0:20:36.04,SR Dialogue,Karasuma,0000,0000,0000,,Your socks still don't match.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.63,0:20:46.60,SR Dialogue,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't screwed up in so long!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.17,0:20:49.74,SR Dialogue,Harima,0000,0000,0000,,Then just what actually happened to her in the past?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.92,0:20:52.10,SR Dialogue,Harima,0000,0000,0000,,Could it possibly be that time?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.03,0:20:55.98,SR Dialogue,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,No, I want to go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.98,0:20:59.59,SR Dialogue,Hanai,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it, do you have no self-awareness as a cyborg?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.59,0:21:00.82,SR Dialogue,Hanai,0000,0000,0000,,Come with me already!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.28,0:21:01.83,SR Dialogue,Hanai,0000,0000,0000,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.83,0:21:03.74,SR Dialogue,Harima,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? She's pretty cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.76,0:21:05.43,SR Dialogue,Harima,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.42,0:21:11.35,SR Dialogue,Harima,0000,0000,0000,,Could that be what caused her amnesia?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.35,0:21:12.65,SR Dialogue,Hanai,0000,0000,0000,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.65,0:21:16.49,SR Dialogue,Hanai,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it happened after I, the genius, modified her, so she was fine but...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.49,0:21:18.67,SR Dialogue,Hanai,0000,0000,0000,,she went missing afterward.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.67,0:21:21.07,SR Dialogue,Hanai,0000,0000,0000,,Ha ha ha ha ha ha ha ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.07,0:21:21.88,SR Dialogue,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,Unforgivable.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.24,0:21:23.34,SR Dialogue,Hanai,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.99,0:21:25.05,SR Dialogue,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,Unforgivable.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.17,0:21:27.51,SR Dialogue,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never forgive you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.96,0:21:30.06,SR Dialogue,Tenma,0000,0000,0000,,...for toying around with a maiden's pure heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.06,0:21:31.52,TL NOTES,,0000,0000,0000,,Note: "Otome" means "Maiden"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.78,0:21:37.52,SR Dialogue,Yuuki,0000,0000,0000,,Tenma's maiden circuit is responding! It's activating the Su--bot!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.52,0:21:42.74,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fs30\an7\shad0\fnArno Pro Caption\pos(307,293)}Lowest Underground Level
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.52,0:21:42.74,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fs30\an7\shad0\fnArno Pro Caption\pos(385,434)}Third Hanger
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.54,0:21:42.74,SR Dialogue,Karasuma,0000,0000,0000,,This moment... It has come at last.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.74,0:21:47.91,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fs30\an7\shad0\fnArno Pro Caption\frz270\pos(601,141)}Final Decisive Battle Weapon
